---
---

<section class="setup-section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Choose Your Path</h2>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Start a new project, adopt an existing one, or just ask what to do next.</p>
  <div class="setup-grid">
    <a href="/guides/first-ten-minutes" class="setup-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <span class="command">aios</span>
        <span class="label">Wizard</span>
      </div>
      <p>Guided setup. Answers questions and creates your project step by step.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/getting-started" class="setup-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <span class="command">aios init</span>
        <span class="label">New Project</span>
      </div>
      <p>Create a fresh project with full AIOS structure and workflow kit.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/getting-started" class="setup-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <span class="command">aios adopt</span>
        <span class="label">Existing Project</span>
      </div>
      <p>Add AIOS structure to a project you already have. Never overwrites.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/guides/command-guide" class="setup-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <span class="command">aios next</span>
        <span class="label">Next Step</span>
      </div>
      <p>Read-only. Prints the recommended next step based on your project.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .setup-section {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .setup-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .setup-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-card-start), var(--color-card-end));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .setup-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-strong);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .command {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.625rem;
    background: var(--color-code-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-2);
  }
  .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .setup-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .setup-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .setup-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
